            <title>[PIG-1372] Restore PigInputFormat.sJob for backward compatibility</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-1372</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The preferred method to get the job&apos;s Configuration object would be to use UDFContext.getJobConf(). This jira is to restore PigInputFormat.sJob  (but we will be marking it deprecated and indicating to use UDFContext.getJobConf() instead) to be backward compatible - we can remove it from pig in a future release.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
